<CATEGORY> financial </CATEGORY>
<HEADLINE> London Shares Close Higher / British Stocks  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	LONDON (AP) -- Share prices rose Monday on the London Stock  
Exchange. 
</P>
<P>
	The Financial Times - Stock Exchange 100-Share Index was up  
182.9 points, or 3.1 percent, at 6,123.9. 
</P>
<P>
	Provisional volume was 1.012 billion shares, compared to 1.068  
billion shares Friday. 
</P>
</TEXT>
