about. It hurts children when their parents are put in jail for 
doing wrong. It also hurts them when they are taken out of the home 
because of neglect or abuse. ... But we do what is right even if 
people get hurt because the person who commits a crime has to be 
punished.'' From a former Clinton supporter in Warwick. 
</P>
