	To Gorton:  
</P>
<P>
	--''The point of view that all politicians are liars and  
Washington would be a ghost town if all liars were removed is an 
exaggeration (I hope). Or that all men are adulterous, fallible to 
a few trailer camp tramps or stalkers.'' From Bellevue, Wash. 
</P>
