opinion of how well he has taken care of governmental affairs. My 
husband and I are seniors, Episcopalian. ... We think he should be 
censured -- with a firm smack on those hands that fondled that 
filthy (expletive). ... Sorry to be so blunt.'' From Port Angeles. 
</P>
<P>
